snippet.title: The Social
snippet.description:
Thanks for checking out my channel! If you enjoyed make sure to subscribe for more content!

The Social is the #1 celebrity and drama news channel on Youtube! With a wide variety of Celebrities featured such as Kylie Jenner, Nicki Minaj, The Weekend, Kim Kardashian, Megan Thee Stallion, Cardi B, Ellen Degeneres, Selena Gomez, and Drake you can always count on us for entertaining content. We upload the best and wildest moments from the most popular celebrities so sit back, relax, and enjoy watching The Social!
